{"tid":1579781,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"請珍惜所有係我地活動期間唔落閘閂舖嘅商戶","createTime":"2019-09-18T17:36:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T04:20:06.000Z","uid":205346,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"43574c8a61b0ef4ddffb921362e6b8c9006a9d54","tid":1579781,"uid":205346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T17:36:51.000Z","msg":"今日手足快閃又一城合唱團，吸引咗唔少人聚集，但可以講幾乎全場都冇一間鋪頭落閘<br />\n反觀藍絲搞嘅國歌行動，淘大成個商場都落晒閘咁濟<br />\n<br />\n咁樣已經證明咗商戶對抗爭者嘅信任，對藍絲廢老嘅厭惡，要知道前線職員係對我地百分百信任先會唔落閘照常營業，呢個絕對係佢地係自己崗位上對抗爭者嘅支持<br />\n<br />\n所以請大家多多支持所有抵住壓力，唔落閘閂門嘅商戶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfa0045a72ea023291456d41fbdf40157ddb0810","tid":1579781,"uid":36158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T17:38:01.000Z","msg":"見到d promoter 跟住un同唱 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bf7b75822b4b5f83c4277d3f2c96c03312934f3","tid":1579781,"uid":229369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T17:39:25.000Z","msg":"見到有啲員工行出舖頭門口睇熱鬧<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa79e8473a2b0eeac62c6ffe799af8427a5991dd","tid":1579781,"uid":310898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T17:40:40.000Z","msg":"明眼人就知邊個先會搞破壞，高下立見"},{"pid":"85454fee01b6060edb468d7c01a57eeb60548a4d","tid":1579781,"uid":205346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dfa0045a72ea023291456d41fbdf40157ddb0810","tid":1579781,"uid":36158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T17:38:01.000Z","msg":"見到d promoter 跟住un同唱 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T17:41:41.000Z","msg":"就算冇跟住唱 佢地選擇繼續開門照常營業已經係支持手足嘅表達方式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c99a6fdbf749db410d194b8740881de6a47f6a2","tid":1579781,"uid":263221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T17:59:52.000Z","msg":"<